repo_description: Deploy GraphQL to a FaaS of your choice quickly and easily

schemas.name: starwars.gql
schemas.content:
type Query {
  human(id: ID!): Human
  allHumans: [Human]
  droid(id: ID!): Droid
  allDroids: [Droid]
}

interface Character {
  id: ID!
  name: String
  friends: [Character]
  appearsIn: [Episode]
  secretBackstory: String
}

enum Episode {
  PHANTOM
  CLONES
  SITH
  NEWHOPE
  EMPIRE
  JEDI
  FORCE
  LASTJEDI
}

type Droid implements Character {
  id: ID!
  name: String
  friends: [Character]
  appearsIn: [Episode]
  secretBackstory: String
  primaryFunction: String
}

type Human implements Character {
  id: ID!
  name: String
  friends: [Character]
  appearsIn: [Episode]
  homePlanet: String
  secretBackstory: String
}
